This paper is primarily focused on video object segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with video processing (cs.MM) and the optimization of neural networks (cs.NE).
